{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WT8o5MjHZKjPSEysFFzhBw","type":"tool_result","content":"   240→When a container is kept, record in SQLite: Docker container ID, run ID, project,\n   241→creation time, status. Updated when container is deleted.\n   242→\n   243→### CLI Command\n   244→\n   245→`cloche delete <container-or-run-id>` — accepts Docker container name/ID or run ID.\n   246→Calls daemon via gRPC to remove the container and update the store.\n   247→Single container at a time.\n   248→\n   249→### gRPC\n   250→\n   251→New RPC: `DeleteContainer(container_id)` — daemon calls `docker rm` and updates store.\n   252→\n   253→### Dashboard\n   254→\n   255→Run detail page shows whether container is still available. If so, shows \"Delete\n   256→container\" button. Project overview shows count of retained containers.\n   257→\n   258→---\n   259→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5a14ceff-57e3-4625-8d3d-726e573e90a0","uuid":"5e7ad6f7-2fa1-427b-863d-950e91083c41","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-03-03-next-features-design.md","content":"When a container is kept, record in SQLite: Docker container ID, run ID, project,\ncreation time, status. Updated when container is deleted.\n\n### CLI Command\n\n`cloche delete <container-or-run-id>` — accepts Docker container name/ID or run ID.\nCalls daemon via gRPC to remove the container and update the store.\nSingle container at a time.\n\n### gRPC\n\nNew RPC: `DeleteContainer(container_id)` — daemon calls `docker rm` and updates store.\n\n### Dashboard\n\nRun detail page shows whether container is still available. If so, shows \"Delete\ncontainer\" button. Project overview shows count of retained containers.\n\n---\n","numLines":20,"startLine":240,"totalLines":269}}}
